Ranger Help for: quarry
=======================

SYNTAX:      quarry
             quarry rock
USAGE:       Hills, mountain, underground
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     10 sp
SKILL TYPE:  utility

SUMMARY:
This command lets a Ranger gather a few useful rocks from rocky terrain
for crafting and sharpening. It stores fieldstone and flint in the
Ranger's wildcraft pouch instead of creating loose rocks in inventory.
It is meant to support skills like 'sharpen', 'make tools', and
'mix weapon paste' without pretending that every room's exposed stone
can be used directly as inventory.

You must already know how to sharpen a weapon before you can use quarry.
